1. The following areas are added to Schedule 1 to section 126 of the Act:

1. County of Kent.

1.1 County of Middlesex.

2. County of Simcoe.

3. District of Kenora.

4. District of Thunder Bay.

5. The Regional Municipality of Hamilton-Wentworth.

6. The Regional Municipality of Peel.

7. The Regional Municipality of Sudbury. O. Reg. 922/93, s. 1; O. Reg. 441/97, s. 1.
